name: WAS The Last of Us
description:
This is a bit of a experiment as many of the TI's I tried failed and cost several days of work. In the end I did a bit of a mix between Subject and Style, combined with prompt mixing.

Samples generated on Protogen v2.2

How to use:

It's best to use this as a mix-in with a subject. For example, with a woman you would do (woman mixed with (tloustyle))

The model has a bias with trying to produce girls, which is odd considering there was like 2 female infected subjects trained on. Anyways, to defeat this, when doing a man, you may need to add negative prompt such as ((female, woman, girl))

modelVersions.name: The Last of Us - HBO Intro Style
modelVersions.description:
This is a bonus style based on the HBO intro sequence. This didn't give me the effect I wanted unfortunately and didn't like it, but others may.

You can use it almost alone to generate cool images based on the intro sequence though. Kinda neat I guess.

Usage:

  1. art by TLOUCord-16500

  2. art by [((TLOUCord-16500)):0.5]

  3. art by [(TLOUCord-16500):2.5]
